  "body": "代码比较多，先以口头描述。\r\n场景：在桥接component（ <carousel> 继承自**WXVContainer**）的过程中，希望动态的改变component中子view的大小。子view 定义在文件中\r\n```script\r\n  <carousel class=\"slider\" scroll-direction=\"horizontal\" show-scrollbar=false if=\"{{item.promotionItems}}\" >\r\n                    <!-- scroller内部再包一层div 计算其需要的宽度 否则在android上无法滚动 -->\r\n                        <div repeat=\"{{promotionItem in item.promotionItems}}\" >\r\n                            <div class=\"itemContainer\">\r\n                                <image src=\"{{promotionItem.img + '!320x320.jpg' + '?webp=0'}}\" class=\"image\"></image>\r\n                                <div class=\"desc\">\r\n                                    <text class=\"todaytitle\">{{promotionItem.promotion_title}}</text>\r\n                                    <!-- 倒计时单独拿出 方便控制 -->\r\n                                    <countdown if=\"{{is_over}}\" begin=\"{{promotionItem.gmt_begin}}\" end=\"{{promotionItem.gmt_end}}\" index=\"{{$index}}\"></countdown>\r\n                                    <text class=\"title\">{{promotionItem.title}}</text>\r\n                                    <div class=\"line\"></div>\r\n                                    <div class=\"priceback\">\r\n                                        <text class=\"symbol\">¥</text>\r\n                                        <text class=\"price\">{{promotionItem.price / 100}}</text>\r\n                                        <text class=\"price_ori\">¥{{promotionItem.price_ori / 100}}</text>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>  \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>    \r\n                </carousel>\r\n```\r\n\r\n执行代码后，ui不变化，通过ddms发现子view的容器本身的大小变化了，展示出来的大小却没有变化。\r\n\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/8480050/19888629/daeb4790-a06a-11e6-813e-dac0a8f537cc.png)\r\n\r\n",
